# Frontend Standards

## Allowed Scope
- `src/**`

## Forbidden Scope
- `functions/**`
- `docs/**` (except tiny inline comments in code when needed)

## Priorities
- Keep UI behavior aligned to accepted specs in `docs/specs/`.
- Handle loading, error, and empty states explicitly.
- Preserve accessibility and predictable interactions.
- Keep UI logic focused; avoid mixing cloud function internals into components.

## Boundary Enforcement
- If backend behavior must change, hand off to `backend-gemschi`.
- Keep edits limited to requested frontend surfaces.
